law.catch_line: Licensure and certification until July 15, 1995, of applicants certified under prior law.
law.text: For a period of one (1) year from July 15, 1994, the board shall issue a license to an applicant who is currently certified as a dietitian and a certificate to an applicant who is currently certified as a nutritionist.
law.history: Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 319, sec. 10, effective July 15, 1994.
